source:
TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_SEQ_00 Quest Sync
Utpala would help the healers do their duty.
target:
TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_SEQ_00Règle spéciale:  synchronisation de quête
Utpala semble s'inquiéter pour quelqu'un.
TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_TODO_00<tab>Parler à la soigneuse du village

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_TODO_02<tab>Pick up the crate of medicine.
TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_TODO_03<tab>Deliver the crate of medicine to the Palaka healer.

TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_UTPALA_100_000<tab>Might you have a few moments to spare? Our healers are overwhelmed with the number of injured and sick, and even a single pair of hands will go a long way toward easing their burden.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_UTPALA_100_000<tab>Excusez-moi, auriez-vous quelques instants pour aider la soigneuse du village<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_UTPALA_100_001<tab>Some of their duties require them to venture into the jungle─a dangerous prospect at the best of times, but a death sentence under current conditions. Perhaps you could lend them your aid?
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_UTPALA_100_001<tab>Elle a besoin d'être escortée dans la forêt, mais je ne sais pas me battre... Pour vous, par contre, ce serait du gâteau, non<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_UTPALA_100_002<tab>If you would offer your capable arm to their aid, please do so─they will be all too glad to accept it, I'm sure.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_UTPALA_100_002<tab>En ce moment, elle porte assistance aux villageois. Si vous lui proposez votre aide, je peux vous dire qu'elle sera plus que soulagée<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_UTPALA_100_003<tab>The healers are doing their best to administer to the sick and wounded, but they are stretched to their breaking point. Offer your aid and I'm sure they'll put you to work straightaway.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_UTPALA_100_003<tab>La soigneuse est en train de porter assistance aux villageois. Si vous lui proposez votre aide, je peux vous dire qu'elle sera plus que soulagée<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_DOCTOR04258_000_005<tab>What? You're here to help? Of course, I am glad for any assistance afforded to me. I have just the task for one such as you, in fact.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_DOCTOR04258_000_005<tab>Salut<var 1D /var>! C'est toi qui es là pour m'aider<var 1D /var>? Parfait, ne perdons pas de temps.

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_DOCTOR04258_000_006<tab>In troubled times such as these, it is ever the medicine which first runs dry. I've sent an assistant to procure a resupply from the Great Work, but apparently she's run into a bit of trouble on her way back.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_DOCTOR04258_000_006<tab>Je n'ai plus assez de remèdes. L'assistante chargée de me ravitailler au Grand Œuvre m'a contactée par linkperle...

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_DOCTOR04258_000_007<tab>It seems something is preventing her from completing the delivery, although she was scarce on the details. Unfortunately, circumstances being what they are, we haven't been able to spare a single person to send to her aid.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_DOCTOR04258_000_007<tab>Il semble qu'elle soit coincée sur le chemin du retour. J'irais bien la chercher moi-même mais j'ai des patients à soigner ici.

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_DOCTOR04258_100_007<tab>Until now, that is! Travel to the Wakeful Torana, where my assistant awaits, and see if you can't solve this little conundrum she's encountered.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_DOCTOR04258_100_007<tab>Elle est coincée sur le chemin du retour, pas loin du Torana veilleur. Va la rejoindre et prête-lui main forte, s'il te plaît.

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_DOCTOR04258_000_008<tab>She is stuck near the Wakeful Torana for some reason that yet eludes me. Please, go there and see if you can't get that medicine into the right hands.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_DOCTOR04258_000_008<tab>Mon assistante est coincée sur le chemin du retour, pas loin du Torana veilleur. Va la rejoindre et prête-lui main forte, s'il te plaît.

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_ASSISTANT04258_000_010<tab>Are you here to help? Thank the gods. Apologies for the imposition, but I just can't carry these supplies any further. I'm afraid my constitution doesn't allow for such strenuous labor.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_ASSISTANT04258_000_010<tab>Ouf... Merci... J'ai trop tiré sur la corde, si je puis dire. Je n'arrive plus à avancer...

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_ASSISTANT04258_000_011<tab>You look to have a stout pair of legs under you─could you deliver the medicine in my stead? I must rest... Yes, just a bit of a lie down.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_ASSISTANT04258_000_011<tab>J'ai été prévenue par linkperle de ta venue, et je me demandais si tu accepterais de rapporter les herbes au village à ma place...<var 1D /var>? J'ai encore besoin de me reposer un peu, mais les remèdes ne peuvent pas attendre.

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_ASSISTANT04258_000_012<tab>It's all in this crate here. Please hurry─the people of Palaka's Stand are in dire need. Would that I had more strength to give...
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_ASSISTANT04258_000_012<tab>Prends <var 33 ((EObj)) 07F61EB4600202 /var> et apporte-la à la soigneuse, je te prie.

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_SYSTEM_000_013<tab>Deliver the medicine crate to the healer awaiting you at Palaka's Stand.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_SYSTEM_000_013<tab>Vous devez transporter <var 33 ((EObj)) 03F61EB4600202 /var> jusqu'à l'Écoute des Palaka, et la donner à la soigneuse du village avant la fin du temps imparti.

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_SYSTEM_000_014<tab>You will have four minutes to complete the task. Should you fail, return to the starting location and begin anew.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_SYSTEM_000_014<tab>Vous pouvez porter cette charge pendant 240 secondes. Vous échouerez si vous n'arrivez pas à temps à destination, et devrez reprendre au point de départ.

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_SYSTEM_000_015<tab>Be wary of attacks from enemies, which will sap your strength.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_SYSTEM_000_015<tab>Le temps restant diminuera si vous recevez des coups. À vous donc d'éviter les combats en route.

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_ASSISTANT04258_000_016<tab>Please, hurry. The sooner the medicine is delivered, the sooner the sick and wounded can be treated.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_ASSISTANT04258_000_016<tab>Prends <var 33 ((EObj)) 03F61EB4600202 /var> et apporte-la à la soigneuse, je te prie.

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_DOCTOR04258_000_017<tab>Oh, you're back. The medicine appears nowhere to be seen, however...
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_DOCTOR04258_000_017<tab>Euh... Il me semblait que tu devais m'apporter une caisse de médicaments...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_DOCTOR04258_000_020<tab>Thank you for picking up the slack, so to speak. I must remember that not all of my assistants are fit for such demanding labor.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_DOCTOR04258_000_020<tab>Mon assistante m'a prévenue, merci de m'avoir apporté la caisse.

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_DOCTOR04258_000_021<tab>I will administer this medicine to those in need as soon as I can. It was Utpala who entreated you to help me, yes? Pray inform her that all is well, and give her my gratitude.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_DOCTOR04258_000_021<tab>Je vais de ce pas m'occuper des patients. C'est Utpala qui a loué tes services, n'est-ce pas<var 1D /var>? Elle devait beaucoup s'inquiéter pour moi, tu peux aller la rassurer et la remercier<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_DOCTOR04258_100_021<tab>It was Utpala who entreated you to help me, yes? Pray inform her that all is well, and give her my gratitude.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_DOCTOR04258_100_021<tab>C'est Utpala qui a loué tes services, n'est-ce pas<var 1D /var>? Elle devait beaucoup s'inquiéter pour moi, tu peux aller la rassurer et la remercier<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_UTPALA_100_022<tab>You've been out for quite a while. I trust the healer has kept you busy?
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_UTPALA_100_022<tab>Merci pour votre aide. J'ai vu que vous aviez pu livrer la caisse à la soigneuse<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_UTPALA_100_023<tab>Oh, she knows who I am!? Well...all I did was pass information along. But if she sends her thanks, then who am I to deny them?
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_UTPALA_100_023<tab>Me remercier<var 1D /var>? Ah, je suis heureuse d'avoir pu être utile, même si je n'ai fait que vous demander votre aide<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_UTPALA_100_024<tab>The healers have barely had a wink of sleep as of late. I'm no fighter, nor do I have a mind for healing, but I'm happy to help where I can. Here, take this for your kind service.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF003_04258_UTPALA_100_024<tab>La soigneuse et son assistante ont travaillé très dur ces derniers temps... Je devrais peut-être leur apporter une petite douceur pour les encourager. Tenez, voici votre récompense.
